title: Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn Episode 6- Two Worlds, Two Tomorrows
description:
The sixth Episode of Mobile Suit Gundam unicorn.

Standard-res, Japanese audio and English hardsubs.

mp4 format.

If you'd rather wait for a hi-res version, you're welcome to do so. This is more of a get your fix and then get the 1080p version later.

If you do download it, I'd appreciate it if you seed.	

This is a re-upload of my previous version, because I apparently can't seed the first one.
